## Prior Art Statement

While rotary valve concepts exist in various forms, this specific 
combination is believed to be novel:

- Intake and exhaust sharing a single central tube path in opposing flows
- Thermal self-regulation through opposing flow as the primary sealing 
  strategy (not materials-based)
- Two/four stroke cycle switching via gear ratio alone
- Crankshaft-as-valve-tube radial configuration (geometric timing lock)

Physical prototypes exist predating this documentation.

This document establishes the date of documentation and sufficient 
technical detail to constitute prior art.

